5 cleric) 65 Mage, 63 Necro, 62 Wizard and a 65 Druid with a frog pet.  I've never seen mobs die that fast before.  It's hillarious to look at the mob while the nukes are landing, reminds me of getting hit by the rocket launcher in Quake.  Boom boom boom dead.  I was so used to it taking 5 minutes and a million mana to kill these same mobs with a conventional group.  <br>
